## Limitations

This report is based on available online resources and may not encompass all perspectives on the impact of cell phones. The findings are limited to the information provided by the selected sources, which may not cover every aspect of the topic comprehensively. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of technology means that new developments may not be reflected in this report.